<HEAD>Mail to Guatemala Halted</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Mail to Guatemala is being halted because of
labor unrest in that Central American country, the U.S. Postal
Service announced.
   Postal officials said Tuesday that the embargo was requested by
the Guatemala postal administration.
