stealth bomber and require the Pentagon to restructure the program.
   A ``yes'' vote is a vote to limit production money.
   Voting yes were 208 Democrats and 49 Republicans.
   Voting no were 38 Democrats and 122 Republicans.
   Y is yes. N is no. X denotes those not voting.
   Present denotes those who voted they were ``present'' at the
time of the vote but did not vote ``yes'' or ``no'' on the issue.
   There are 3 vacancies in the 435-member House.
